																		And your toys are my toys and my toys are your toys
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6479803); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6479803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226982" alt="HarryBlank" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6479803)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6479803); return false;" >HarryBlank</a></span> <span class="odate time_1601583406 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">01 Oct 2020 20:16</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4786421">
									

<p>You might think writing something like this would be a lot of fun.</p>
<p>You might, in fact, think writing something like this would be a non-stop fun-fest, the best thing a writer could possibly do with their spare time.</p>
<p>You'd be right.</p>
<p>Thanks to my TEAM RR BEST TEAM: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/karakatt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5950867); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5950867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602722191" alt="KaraKatt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5950867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/karakatt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5950867); return false;">KaraKatt</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602722191" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;">not_a_seagull</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-pighead" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3242824); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3242824&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602722191" alt="The Pighead" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3242824)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-pighead" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3242824); return false;">The Pighead</a></span>, and thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4558017&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602722191" alt="Grigori Karpin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4558017)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;">Grigori Karpin</a></span> for being so complimentary it was, frankly, suspicious.</p>
<p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/boogey-man23" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2362395); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2362395&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602722191" alt="Boogey_Man23" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2362395)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/boogey-man23" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2362395); return false;">Boogey_Man23</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nickthebrick1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5208936); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5208936&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602722191" alt="Nickthebrick1" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5208936)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nickthebrick1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5208936); return false;">Nickthebrick1</a></span> for letting me borrow their cool truck, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3187823); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602722191" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3187823); return false;">CadaverCommander</a></span> for letting me take that awesome suit for a spin.</p>
<p>Special thanks as well to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-dan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(453417); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=453417&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602722191" alt="Dr Dan" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=453417)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-dan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(453417); return false;">Dr Dan</a></span> for, via absence, allowing me to hijack his author avatar. If he finds out, I hope he doesn't hate it.</p>
