			<div class="content" id="post-content-4786452">
									

<p>I love the setting you got here! The little sigils between every segment, a wide variety of unique anomalies, oh and that conversation between the Redd Mennace and the Moon Champion&#8230; absolutely amazing!</p>
<p>I trends the line between absurd and tense just enough to make me smile. Wonder if we get an anime-like fight scene between the vengeful fire truck or the lunatic spaceman?</p>
<p>Also poor Dr. Dan. At this rate he'll probably die of a brain aneurysm from all the stress.</p>

