					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6479803); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6479803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226982" alt="HarryBlank" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6479803)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6479803); return false;" >HarryBlank</a></span> <span class="odate time_1601589019 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">01 Oct 2020 21:50</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4786464">
									

<p>I'm very, very glad you liked it, particularly as you're something of a stakeholder :P I combed the mainsite for stuff that's at Site-19, and nearly fainted when Bigg Redd came up, I was so excited. One of my favourites, and I could use him! So yes, you can expect something truly ridiculous between the Mennace and the lunatic at the beginning of the next tale. Your skip's vote count is missing at least one digit, in my opinion. Maybe two. <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4601">GO READ 4601 EVERYBODY</a>.</p>
<p>This was so much fun to write, it's indecent. I'm hooked.</p>
<p>Also glad you liked the sigils, I dinked around with that stuff for a long time trying to find something I liked. Feels like taking control of more aspects of the process, and it's very satisfying.</p>
<p>Dan's got a hard couple of days ahead of him. But he might just die laughing.</p>
<p>Thanks for the great feedback and kind words :D</p>

