														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4787103">
									

<p>This tale is really good for most of its length and then Moon Champion shows up. Dr. Dan is a fantastic character because his ingenuity and confidence in setting anomalies against each other feel grounded in the setting of Rez. Moon Champion — and <a href="/scp-4494">SCP-4494</a>, for that matter — is too goofy for this setting. It’s like putting Bugs Bunny in a Marvel movie.</p>

