														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4787260">
									

<p>Those are two of my major goals, here: tell a story about a clever Dan putting out fires with brainpower alone, and expose some great stuff to new readers. Some of what I'm using has vote counts in the thousands; a lot of it is deeply underrated, and I can't recommend that stuff enough. If any of these anomalies intrigued you or made you chuckle, follow them links! I won't claim to have some sort of univeral taste, but if I gave a full scene to a skip, I do feel confident recommending it.</p>
<p>Thanks for enjoying it, I'm having a blast.</p>

